      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SHE SAID SO (7) found some support last start but struggled into sixth (20.77), beaten 10 lengths. Finished third the start before. Has performed well from this box with a win and two minor placings to her name from four starts. Has ability and is a key runner. MY BOY MAJESTIC (4) was safely held last time out, finishing sixth at Taree Super Track over 300m behind Awesome Return (17.90) in a Grade 5. Comes through a solid form race last start. Can do much better this time. DYNAMIC REBEL (2) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing eighth (18.11) in a Grade 4/5 at Taree Super Track. Solid record here winning three races. The form from her last run is stacking up nicely. Great chance to atone. MYTHIC (8) is always a threat when he draws this box.",
